  characterName: Dr. Sturgeon
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3cadb61783a8ad44abb478954be17e5d, type: 3}
  lines:
  - As wet as you make me. Perch will always have my heart.
  - You won't be around much longer anyway.
  - Thank you for all the money you are brining in you juicy man.
  - The Great Dribble Church and it's followers will put it to great use.
